粮」当鸥粮在公园售卖？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-57f370ca0590aa34faa499a520776497_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "117 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/500464929"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I96/lgMXU4YhtEAMaCDczNDk1NzI4ILTm5owGMAw4d0AZcgk1MDA0NjQ5Mjl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1637647752.3581932", "card_id": "Q_500368524", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 24}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《英雄联盟双城之战》中杰斯拿金克丝交换祖安独立的做法？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a2c2ab7ee920655d38e3477b0a8a025e_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "117 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/500368524"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I96/lgMXU4YhtEAMaCDczNDc0MzIzINbE44wGMAA4LkAacgk1MDAzNjg1MjR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1637647752.358599", "card_id": "Q_465646312", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 571}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有没有三观很正的文案?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-0e63a08be74f62758f7bd2bcb78fded2_720w.jpg?source=2044ae36"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "113 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/465646312"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I96/lgMXU4YhtEAMaCDY1NzU2NjAyIPnQrYYGMA44ziNAG3IJNDY1NjQ2MzEyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1637647752.359019", "card_id": "Q_500659387", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 63}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "湖北一女子跳楼去世，曾与「遛狗不牵绳」业主发生纷争，其父称警方暂未立案，业主需要承担法律责任吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "最新进展： 武汉坠楼女子父亲：代价太大，警方未立案 11 月 22 日，卢某林父亲向记者介绍，女儿性格活泼开朗，承受能力很强，但这次与狗狗主人们的冲突持续了 2 个多月。在接到女儿去世消息时，感觉就像晴天霹雳，「她拿生命来控告，但是这个代价太大了」。卢先生称，目前警方暂未立案，涉事狗狗主人并未道歉，物业也未有明确答复，希望能还女儿一个公道。武汉坠楼女子家属称警方未立案 父亲：代价太大，警方未立案 11 月 19 日，武汉 36 岁的女子卢孝林坠楼第七天，小区上百名业主自发在草地上铺满鲜花悼念。这是一处有着 1600 多户的大型小区，业主们前来悼念的同时，想以此表达对小区里狗扰民问题的不满。 据悉，她出事前多次在业主群反映，因被宠物狗追逐与几名狗主人口角，之后矛盾冲突两个多月，曾被对方围堵辱骂棍打，她曾购买打狗棍反击，并留言要「以命相抗」。有邻居称，曾见她在楼下被狗主人用长棍打。 在简短的遗书中，她把喜爱的物品做了列表，全部送给了朋友。目前，家属已将相关资料递交警方并正式报案。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-55985331436bf4a28df3b9c08bee345d_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "112 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/500659387"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I96/lgMXU4YhtEAMaCDczNTM4OTk5IKrk64wGMAI4vAFAHHIJNTAwNjU5Mzg3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1637647752.359752", "card_id": "Q_500141325", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 50}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "问下大家，北漂每月能攒下钱吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c4d54c707489775917283eab5f713fae_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "108 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/500141325"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I96/lgMXU4YhtEAMaCDczNDIzODY1IKOe3owGMAI4YEAdcgk1MDAxNDEzMjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1637647752.360189", "card_id": "Q_499536826", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 32}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "上海乐高乐园正式开工，会和迪士尼、环球影城形成三足鼎立局面吗？你更喜欢哪个主题乐园？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "11 月 17 日, 上海乐高乐园度假区项目在金山区枫泾镇举行开工仪式。 据悉，上海乐高乐园度假区位于金山区枫泾镇东部，占地面积达 31.8 万平方米，预计于 2024 年开园。 仪式当天首次公布了上海乐高乐园 8 大片区，包含乐高中心大楼、积木街道、乐高积木、乐高城市、乐高小伙伴、悟空小侠、乐高忍者、乐高城堡，其中「悟空小侠」为全球首发主题园区。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-2df56799359575342f15f6685aa259a3_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": 